\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where you've stood on the edge and ledge of the thing God was asking of you.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Stay in a marriage where you were not happy\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Give a large amount that was going to be a huge sacrifice but you didn't want to or you weren't sure you had enough\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}leave an unhealthy friendship that you've had for years\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Or, walk away from a habit or hangup that has held you captive and hurts you but if you're being honest...in the short run you feel better and that becomes the goal.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The question that all of us ask in these moments is WHO is this God that is asking me to do this THING.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Can I trust Him and do I really know Him.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so last week we started a new series and discussed how God has a name\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}(recap the last week and the importance and difference between a Title and a Name)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}You can even pull up the points if you need to fill in a little time.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading20\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And while YHWH is His name...He is more than a name...He has a reputation...He has attributes. He has a personality that we can rely on in good and bad times.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And this week we're going to look into the first and most important attribute of who God is.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In fact this attribute is the one that influences every other attribute.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And we find it in a story...\
