\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(Here the Hebrew is ha\'92el haqqadosh \'96 \'93the Holy God.\'94)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}No I didn't just say Haagen-Daz...that's ice cream...is God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I said ha\'92el haqqadosh (pronounced Ha Kadosh)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is this word that Paul preached on a few weeks ago...Holy\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It means a few things but for today...it means to be set apart...to be different...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The best definition is the one I want to use today...it means this...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To be OTHER.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Which may not help and that is sort of why I like it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}The definition helps a little bit but it doesn't answer all the questions you might have and that allows us to keep God as God and us as us.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}In fact I love this quote about God...\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading20\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 The moment God is figured out with nice neat lines and definitions, we are no longer dealing with God - Rob Bell\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So part of this journey is not so much about putting lines and boxes around God but allowing what do know to help us process and be ok with what we don't know.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So we are left with this idea that the most important characteristic about God is that He is OTHER. He is someone who is outside of our understanding and what we can comprehend...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And if you're really paying attention...you might be asking...then why are we studying this?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I can't know what it is...how is this going to help me understand who God is so I can do what God says?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Well...I think the author of Isaiah was asking the same thing...because about 50 chapters later...it's like he gets back around to talking about the practical application of what this Holy God is all about...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In Isaiah 55 the author again in verse 5 speaks to this God YHWH who is HOLY...and then he says this about what God thinks...\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 Isaiah 55:8-9\
8\'a0\'93For 
\f0\b my thoughts 
\f1\b0 are not 
\f0\b your thoughts\cf0 ,\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He is saying that the way in which God thinks about a situation...isn't how you're going to think about a situation...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It's not even close\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You will look at a situation and you're going to see it from your vantage point...from your point of view...that is not the point of view that God has..\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God will see your point of view...their point of view...the worlds point of view...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If that wasn't enough - He can see it from a historical point of view\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He can see it from a future point of view\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He can see it from any and all angles you can think of...and more!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His thoughts are not your thoughts!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And that should be obvious...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}but every time you stand on that edge of what God wants you to do...and you question not WHAT He said but IS He good...you need to remember this...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your Thoughts are not God's Thoughts\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But he goes on just to reinforce the point...\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \uc0\u8232 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0neither are 
\f0\b your ways my ways,
\f1\b0 \'94\uc0\u8232 declares the Lord.\
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It's not just how you think about a situation but how you would act...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Isaiah is reminding us that God's unique awareness leads to a unique action\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His ways are not your ways!\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration - One of the hardest situations I find myself in as a pastor is counseling someone who is in a broken marriage. It is broken and one or both are miserable. No one has cheated thankfully but what that means is that according to how God thinks, there is no way out. I have been asked multiple times...why would God want me to be stuck in a broken terrible marriage where neither of us are happy...doesn't God want me to be happy? (you can use a different story if you want here)\
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My answer is always the same...I don't know.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Translation - God's ways are higher than my ways - God's thoughts are higher than my thoughts.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I can trust in either my ways or God's ways but they many times will not be the same.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(sit here for a second if you need to)\
